descriptionNullable:
**ISIC 2019 Classification training dataset. Images resized to 224x224 for Melanoma Skin Cancer Detection.**
## Files
- **train-image/** - image files for the training set (provided for train only)
- **train-metadata.csv** - metadata for the training set

## Columns included only in train-metadata.csv
| Field Name | Description |
| --- | --- |
| `target` | Binary class {0: benign, 1: malignant}. |
| `patient_id` | Randomly generated for formatting |
| `isic_id` | Unique identifier for images |
